doc.title: Zosintha zomwe zilipo
doc.page: : Ulalo ndi chinthu chomwe chili patsamba latsambali kuti mudziwe zambiri, onani
doc.isSameSubDomain: {{_isSameSubDomain_}}: Dzina la domeni lomwelo, ngakhale mayina akuluakulu a {{_youtube_}} ndi {{_families_}} onse ndi {{_mainDomain_}}, mayina a subdomain ndi {{_youtubeSubDomain_}} ndi {{ _familiesSubDomain_}} motsatana, mayina awo amasiyana.
doc.minimatch: : {{_glob_}} njira yofananira, pogwiritsa ntchito laibulale ya {{_minimatch_}}, njira yogwiritsira ntchito <a href='https://github.com/isaacs/minimatch' target='_blank' rel='noreferrer'>Onani < /a>, kapena mutha kusaka {{_glob_}}.
doc.isSameDomain: : Kaya ndi dzina lomwelo, {{_zoona_}} ndi inde, {{_false_}} ayi.

doc.isPageSublink: : Ngati tsamba lapanoli ndi tsamba laling'ono la ulalo womwe wadina, {{_zoona_}} ndi inde, {{_false_}} ayi.
